subproject.description:
Output 1: Strengthened capacity of CABC in institutional developing, organizational streamlining, function broadening, service diversification and partnership building etc.

Output 2: CABC Secretariat is able to perform in full scale its functions and diversified services, through which generating regular income to support its operations.

Output 3:  Proactive support given to CABC for its network building in Africa, which contributes to information collection as well as contact facilitation for Sino-African business development.
subproject.title: Capacity Building of the China

subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
